comment: Bogut (GSW) is in a legal guarding position and contact with Mozgov (CLE) is incidental to his effort to defend him.

L-Slash and RATR angles show that after receiving the ball, Mozgov (CLE) dribbles once and then lands with a jump stop where his R foot comes down first (Step 1) and then his L foot comes down (Step 2). The spin constitutes additional steps.
Bogut (GSW) makes contact with Mozgov's (CLE) arm and the contact affects his shot.
Thompson's (CLE) contact is incidental to his effort to defend Green's (GSW) shot.
Thompson (CLE) is moving toward Curry (GSW) and makes contact on the jump shot.
Green (GSW) does not make contact with Mozgov (CLE).
Irving (CLE) is moving toward Curry (GSW) and makes contact on the jump shot.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Curry (GSW) was inside the three-point arc (attempting a two-point shot) when he was fouled was upheld.
Curry (GSW) cleanly strips the ball from James (CLE).
Jones (CLE) grabs Iguodala's (GSW) arm as he attempts to secure the ball.
Jones (CLE) moves into Iguodala's (GSW) path after he has started his upward shooting motion.
Thompson (CLE) gets into a legal screening position before contact with Curry (GSW).
Smith (CLE) commits a take foul on Green (GSW).
Jones (CLE) gets tangled with Barnes (GSW) and makes incidental contact as both stumble to the floor.
